item.title: Zenithscape Client error help
item.dc:creator: @qeruina qeruina
item.description:
@qeruina wrote:

Go to your computer\programfiles\java\jdk####
The #### is your Java Jdk version, then go to your client and right click, edit and you should see something like this: "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.8.0_11\bin\java.exe"
Change the jdk1.8.0_11 to your version, then close, compile and TADAAAA
